"Review individual lessons to make sure curriculum-level learning "
"objectives are being met by the set of lessons."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/lesson_development/lesson_development_roles.md:28
msgid ""
"Prepare the workshop homepage repository for lesson release. Curriculum "
"Advisors will be listed as Editors for this repository at release."
msgstr ""

